<paragraph id="IFRS16_C17" base="F45930966"><paranum>C17</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 16"/><data name="paranum" value="C17"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS16_P0667">If a sale and leaseback transaction was accounted for as a sale and a <xref base="SL45930039" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0354">finance lease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0122"/></ph></xref> applying IAS 17, the seller-<xref base="F45929736" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0380">lessee<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0220"/></ph></xref> shall:</p><ol id="IFRS16_L0073" base="F45930969" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IFRS16_P0668" base="F45930970">account for the leaseback in the same way as it accounts for any other finance lease that exists at the date of initial application; and</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p id="IFRS16_P0669" base="F45930992">continue to amortise any gain on sale over the <xref base="F45929725" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0376">lease term<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0218"/></ph></xref>.</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>